nodes.text: Star Wars: Rogue Squadron: X-Wing vs. Tie Fighter

Star Wars Rogue Squadron: X-Wing vs. Tie Fighter was a planned Star Wars game for the Wii console. The title would have been a massively multiplayer RPG with warring factions, on the side of the Empire and the Rebellion. The project was intended as an Xbox launch title, and development was underway when the project was canceled, LucasArts being dubious of creating a launch title for the system.
